Install:
java -version >> 17
Android Studio
Flutter

Cmd: 
	flutter --version
	flutter doctor >> to check installaion
-------
Add packages under pubspec.yaml
    >> under Dependencies

    run >> flutter pub get
        >> flutter pub upgrade --major-versions

Flutter run key commands.
r Hot reload. 
R Hot restart.
h List all available interactive commands.
d Detach (terminate "flutter run" but leave application running).
c Clear the screen
q Quit (terminate the application on the device).



